window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>One knife to take a life. One breath to honor Death.</b></p> <p>Dustin Graves can’t get a break. Murdering an Old One was only the beginning. Enraged, the Eldest have answered with searing rains of ivory fire from the stars, threatening Valero and the world itself. The madness must be stopped.</p> <p>Ancient gods of prophecy, death, and darkness themselves answer the call for battle. But the secret to saving the world lies closer to Dustin's heart than he knows: a ritual sacrifice, meant to end the suffering. After all...what’s one life against the fate of billions?</p> <p>If you like snarky heroes, snappy dialogue, and a bit of grit and gore, you'll love the sixth book in Nazri Noor's series of urban-fantasy novels. Explore the Darkling Mage universe and discover <i>Last Rites</i> today.</p>"; 
